四世界毁滅. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開啟第五世界.<br />\n霍皮族的還預言&ldquo;當 Kachina 在天空中出現時，第五世界將會出現&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash; 這就是凈化的日子，審判將宣告邪惡和不道德的人死亡。所有的即將遭受的苦難正在來到我們身邊，由於地球母親在疼痛中，所以大地的呼吸挾帶著龍捲風  、洪水和地震 。kachina 是霍皮人崇拜的祖靈, 它是一個精神象徵符號，意味著&ldquo;生命的創造者&rdquo;。這個符號的裝飾物用於在每年冬至或夏至祭祀活動時召喚太陽神的回歸。"},{"pid":"3e192057c8d8792b854309ec129f40c2a4a8efb0","tid":2274360,"uid":281401,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"卡特咪就造就列根<br />\n奧巴馬咪造就侵<br />\n<br />\n永遠就係一個循環<br />\n二戰後，不斷就係民主黨搞到屎咁，<br />\n共和黨執番，跟住又衰過"},{"pid":"15f041c05fbbbd7bb2c9e20cf260a9f5443da14c","tid":2274360,"uid":221035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2b7788b631fe5f3a496adef8aff168a21ce6736","tid":2274360,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJARxL1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJARxL1.png&h=97b17930&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"唔認同嘅位係，中美如果friend返<br />\n繼續係跨國資本得益同壟斷，底層係一定反<br />\n正如白人藍領工人支持特朗普"},{"pid":"d3f0481d8e0c44a63a46f646ba937de0d57e9cbd","tid":2274360,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7dac9fb7b9ee60e718c74a79a88705cda9ac06","tid":2274360,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"問題係要幾多年<br />\n如果要美國一路衰弱落去"},{"pid":"7fadfe578e0ea96d2d92acb9bd4eb6d3a2174db8","tid":2274360,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"我係驚民主黨班高層收晒支那利益而出賣美國咋"},{"pid":"49d567f6dadc3a8a0a6c50ddb1d710188b14b997","tid":2274360,"uid":287027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee98724e2c5b025a83e618eb89bbef9056092708","tid":2274360,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote